<div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">English political theorist</div>
<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1236090951">.mw-parser-output .hatnote{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output div.hatnote{padding-left:1.6em;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .hatnote i{font-style:normal}.mw-parser-output .hatnote+link+.hatnote{margin-top:-0.5em}@media print{body.ns-0 .mw-parser-output .hatnote{display:none!important}}</style>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">This article is about the British political theorist. For the British political sociologist, see <a href="/wiki/David_Miller_(sociologist)" title="David Miller (sociologist)">David Miller (sociologist)</a>. For the British philosopher, see <a href="/wiki/David_Miller_(philosopher)" title="David Miller (philosopher)">David Miller (philosopher)</a>.</div>
